K-Bench Synthetic PII Corpus — License
======================================

The synthetic PII corpus under data/ (entities pii-00000 ... pii-04999 and their
attributes) is released under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
License (CC BY 4.0):

    https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

You are free to share and adapt the material for any purpose, provided you give
appropriate credit to "the K-Bench authors", provide a link to the license, and
indicate if changes were made.

The corpus is entirely synthetic, generated with Python Faker
(scripts/01_generate_pii.py); it describes no real persons. See docs/DATASHEET.md
for provenance, intended use, and prohibited uses.

The benchmark CODE is licensed separately — see ../LICENSE.
